sequenceDiagram
    participant WS as Binance / Solana WS
    participant API as Django ASGI (Uvicorn)
    participant Pydantic as Pydantic v2 Validator
    participant Svc as Risk Engine Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (psycopg3)
    participant Monitor as Grafana

    WS->>API: POST /api/v1/trades/ingest/
    API->>Pydantic: Parse & Strict Validate
    Pydantic-->>API: Validated TradeSchema
    API->>Svc: assess_trade_risk()
    Svc->>Svc: Decimal Math (P&L / AML Check)
    Svc-->>API: RiskAssessment (Score, Reason)
    API->>DB: await Trade.objects.acreate()
    DB-->>Monitor: Raw SQL Metrics
    API-->>WS: 201 Created (TradeSchemaOut)